<title>SRI LANKA: Sri Lanka Hayleys up 5 percent on volume.</title>
<headline>Sri Lanka Hayleys up 5 percent on volume.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares of Hayleys Ltd rose 4.76 percent or 10 rupees to 220 in early Tuesday trade on turnover of 163,000 shares, brokers said.</p>
<p>&quot;Investors were prepared to pay a premium provided they could get a substantial quantity,&quot; said a broker who declined to be identified.</p>
<p>The share fell back to 210 rupees after the volume was traded, he said.</p>
<p>The blue chip Hayleys is one of three diversified conglomerates trading in Colombo.</p>
<p>--Colombo newsroom (941) 434319</p>
